  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This update includes a few quick updates.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.7.4.7-EnterpriseDataFeed\">Enterprise Data Feed</h3><ul><li><p>Fixed an issue related to the new database schema introduced in 1.7.4 which will restore the data feed functionality.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.7.4.7-Dialog/ModalWindows\">Dialog / Modal Windows</h3><ul><li><p>In RepairQ\u00a0there are many cases where a\u00a0dialog / modal window overlays the screen, and some windows would be more effective if they\u00a0covered more vertical space. With this update, window overlays will\u00a0stretch vertically to use more of the browser window.</p></li></ul>",
